high_descs: Turn around to face the table in front of the couch.
Pick up the media device on the table in front of the couch.
Turn to the right to face the couch.
Place the media device on the right side of the couch.
Turn left and walk across the room to the TV stand.
Pick up the media device on the TV stand.
Turn around and walk forward to face the couch.
Place the media device next to the first media device.
anns.task_desc: To gather 2 media devices and place them on the right side of the couch.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the sofa, and then turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the phone on the table.
Turn right to face the grey sofa.
Place the phone to the right of the remote closest to you.
Turn left and walk to the tv stand.
Pick up the cell phone behind the tv on the stand.
Turn around and walk to the grey sofa.
Place the phone to the right of the other phone on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on the grey  sofa.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the edge of the coffee table farthest away from the windows.
Pick up the white smartphone to the left of the gray plate from the coffee table.
Turn to the right and face the right arm of the couch.
Place the smartphone on the couch to the right of the remote control on the edge of the couch cushion.
Turn left and move to the drawers to the left of the fireplace.
Pick up the smartphone from the rear right corner of the drawers, to the right of the television.
Turn left and move to the right arm of the couch.
Place the smartphone on the couch in the area between the smartphone already there and the set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two smartphones on the couch.
